WEBVTT

1
00:00:14.708 --> 00:00:17.666
And now? Where are you rushing off to?

2
00:00:31.791 --> 00:00:34.333
If you think you can run away...

3
00:00:35.041 --> 00:00:37.541
We'll find you.

4
00:01:13.333 --> 00:01:16.458
I'm sure they produce thousands
of bottles of bleach per month.

5
00:01:16.541 --> 00:01:18.583
Tell me. how are we going to do this?

6
00:01:19.875 --> 00:01:21.708
What else is stored in there?

7
00:01:21.791 --> 00:01:23.541
Other products to cover up.

8
00:01:24.291 --> 00:01:26.000
That's where you will start the fire.

9
00:01:26.875 --> 00:01:30.125
I saw a storeroom and an office.

10
00:01:30.208 --> 00:01:32.541
I will find a way to get in
and have a look around.

11
00:01:33.791 --> 00:01:37.333
As long as some product survives for
the cosmetics bureau to investigate.

12
00:01:40.750 --> 00:01:43.125
Uh. Zee. tell me something.

13
00:01:43.625 --> 00:01:46.833
Are you okay? You seem a bit distracted.

14
00:01:46.916 --> 00:01:48.375
No. I'm okay.

15
00:01:48.458 --> 00:01:49.708
And Ndu?

16
00:01:50.291 --> 00:01:51.333
It's over.

17
00:01:53.208 --> 00:01:54.875
Good. That's what I want to hear.

18
00:03:50.500 --> 00:03:51.958
It'll be fun.

19
00:04:29.666 --> 00:04:33.958
Sifiso. please go buy four fat cakes.

20
00:04:34.041 --> 00:04:35.041
Sharp.

21
00:04:40.791 --> 00:04:43.291
Please have a look at this.

22
00:05:18.958 --> 00:05:20.500
You're going out with Zinhle?

23
00:06:18.416 --> 00:06:19.625
Uh. hi.

24
00:06:20.208 --> 00:06:21.208
Hi.

25
00:06:23.666 --> 00:06:25.041
Are you looking for something?

26
00:06:26.916 --> 00:06:27.916
No.

27
00:06:29.583 --> 00:06:32.083
I'm just waiting for Mbali.

28
00:06:34.416 --> 00:06:37.666
Yes. she works at New Point.

29
00:06:37.750 --> 00:06:40.208
- Do you know her?
- I don't know her.

30
00:06:42.458 --> 00:06:43.791
Tell me something.

31
00:06:44.625 --> 00:06:46.166
have we met before?

32
00:06:47.666 --> 00:06:48.750
No.

33
00:06:49.791 --> 00:06:51.375
- Are you sure?
- Yes. I'm sure.

34
00:06:57.708 --> 00:06:59.333
You can't park here.

35
00:07:01.041 --> 00:07:02.041
Sure.

36
00:07:02.958 --> 00:07:03.958
Cheers. sir.

37
00:13:16.916 --> 00:13:19.916
Zinhle. there will be nothing left
if you don't get here soon.

38
00:14:06.458 --> 00:14:07.708
It's you.

39
00:14:08.916 --> 00:14:10.000
It's you.

40
00:14:11.041 --> 00:14:12.250
Hey! Come back.

41
00:15:16.416 --> 00:15:18.333
Hey! Wake up!

42
00:15:28.875 --> 00:15:30.166
The stock is on fire.

43
00:17:32.125 --> 00:17:34.000
What were you doing at the factory?

44
00:17:35.250 --> 00:17:37.750
Don't tell me about Zinhle.
What were you doing at the factory?

45
00:17:37.833 --> 00:17:39.083
What are you talking about?

46
00:17:40.916 --> 00:17:42.583
Mom. what is going on here?

47
00:17:57.208 --> 00:17:58.791
Ndumiso. get in the house.

48
00:18:07.666 --> 00:18:09.666
Phila! Talk! What happened?

49
00:18:17.916 --> 00:18:20.458
I just want to know what happened!

50
00:18:21.458 --> 00:18:22.625
Are you deaf?

51
00:18:23.458 --> 00:18:24.541
Shut up!

52
00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:28.000
Talk!

53
00:18:39.291 --> 00:18:40.875
You're an idiot!

54
00:19:14.541 --> 00:19:16.375
Did you tell Zinhle what it is?

55
00:19:21.541 --> 00:19:22.958
I have to call Angela.

56
00:20:37.416 --> 00:20:38.500
Oh my goodness.

57
00:20:39.500 --> 00:20:40.833
His phone is off.

58
00:22:09.875 --> 00:22:12.583
My father told me
just before he made me CEO.

59
00:22:42.291 --> 00:22:43.750
But is it true or not?

60
00:23:37.833 --> 00:23:38.833
Hey.

61
00:23:39.458 --> 00:23:41.125
<i>We have a problem. Come now.</i>

62
00:23:41.791 --> 00:23:42.791
What happened?

63
00:23:42.875 --> 00:23:44.666
<i>I need you. Zinhle. Now.</i>

64
00:24:09.125 --> 00:24:10.416
Hey. Are you okay?

65
00:24:36.583 --> 00:24:38.083
You can't go on your own.

66
00:24:57.375 --> 00:24:59.000
We need to talk when you come back.

67
00:25:17.041 --> 00:25:18.541
He'll get back to us soon.

68
00:25:49.041 --> 00:25:51.041
He had started his nonsense again.

69
00:25:52.458 --> 00:25:53.583
You know how he is.

70
00:26:01.791 --> 00:26:03.458
After your heart attack.

71
00:26:04.708 --> 00:26:05.958
I thought that...

72
00:26:07.791 --> 00:26:08.791
Yeah?

73
00:26:14.083 --> 00:26:15.958
We met up at the hotel.

74
00:26:19.041 --> 00:26:22.250
I said some harsh things
to him so he'd never try again.

75
00:26:24.791 --> 00:26:25.791
Fool!

76
00:26:25.833 --> 00:26:28.875
Yes. I told him he's a fool
for coming after me all this...

77
00:27:08.625 --> 00:27:10.875
What are we going to do with a hostage?

78
00:27:12.708 --> 00:27:13.916
He saw my face.

79
00:27:14.583 --> 00:27:16.958
The place was on fire.

80
00:27:18.375 --> 00:27:20.625
What if he traced me back to you?

81
00:27:40.541 --> 00:27:41.625
Wait!

82
00:27:42.458 --> 00:27:43.541
Okay. fine.

83
00:27:50.041 --> 00:27:52.041
I knew you when you were a little boy.

84
00:27:53.791 --> 00:27:55.666
The scars on your face.

85
00:28:48.416 --> 00:28:49.583
Look at this.

86
00:29:36.541 --> 00:29:37.541
Where is she?

87
00:29:47.583 --> 00:29:48.583
Go fetch her.

88
00:30:32.083 --> 00:30:34.041
What are we going to do?

89
00:30:41.916 --> 00:30:42.916
It's risky.

90
00:30:43.500 --> 00:30:46.833
But if we pull it off
then it's over for Don and Grace.

91
00:30:54.875 --> 00:30:56.166
Trust me.

92
00:32:03.958 --> 00:32:05.375
What are you doing here?

93
00:32:07.041 --> 00:32:08.291
What's going on here?

94
00:32:09.250 --> 00:32:10.541
Hello. Calvin.

95
00:32:14.333 --> 00:32:15.958
This is my brother.

96
00:32:16.041 --> 00:32:18.458
I was also at the house.

97
00:32:21.500 --> 00:32:24.125
She'd wash off chemicals you used on me.

98
00:32:25.291 --> 00:32:28.708
Do you remember the day
Don Bhengu burnt me?

99
00:32:32.208 --> 00:32:33.208
Do you remember?

100
00:32:35.541 --> 00:32:37.000
Do you remember?!

101
00:32:43.041 --> 00:32:47.000
- What about the fire?
- We managed... to escape.

102
00:32:48.208 --> 00:32:51.208
Me. my brother and my sister.

103
00:32:54.416 --> 00:32:56.666
Our sister. Amahle.

104
00:32:58.166 --> 00:33:01.625
She died in this very room.
seven months ago.

105
00:33:08.166 --> 00:33:10.666
All because of your chemicals.

106
00:33:13.666 --> 00:33:15.250
We escaped the fire.

107
00:33:17.791 --> 00:33:21.625
But we never survived what you did to us.

108
00:33:23.500 --> 00:33:24.625
My brother's body.

109
00:33:26.250 --> 00:33:28.041
My face.

110
00:33:29.041 --> 00:33:30.625
My sister's life.

111
00:33:33.083 --> 00:33:34.166
I'm sorry.

112
00:33:36.416 --> 00:33:37.416
I'm sorry.

113
00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:41.125
If you really mean it. help us.

114
00:33:42.958 --> 00:33:48.625
Help us show the world
what Don and Grace did to us.

115
00:34:59.125 --> 00:35:00.583
It's okay.

116
00:35:00.666 --> 00:35:02.000
You'll heal.

117
00:35:15.041 --> 00:35:19.041
Don and Grace came once a week
to put that cream on us.

118
00:35:21.458 --> 00:35:23.625
But you were there every day.

119
00:35:24.583 --> 00:35:27.666
You used to bathe us.
You'd feed us and put us to sleep.

120
00:35:29.125 --> 00:35:30.458
You cared for us.

121
00:35:39.041 --> 00:35:40.333
I'm begging you.

122
00:36:07.625 --> 00:36:08.750
You'll help us.

123
00:36:10.375 --> 00:36:11.791
Let me go.

124
00:37:01.208 --> 00:37:03.958
Don and Grace'll throw you to the dogs.

125
00:37:05.208 --> 00:37:07.166
Are you still going to help them?

126
00:37:08.125 --> 00:37:10.375
Unlock his phone and let's call Grace.

127
00:37:11.791 --> 00:37:12.958
What's the PIN?

128
00:37:59.625 --> 00:38:00.625
Are you okay?

129
00:38:03.750 --> 00:38:05.583
Have you seen what's been happening?

130
00:38:10.000 --> 00:38:12.708
<i>You're the only one
who can make this go away.</i>

131
00:38:28.416 --> 00:38:32.250
Don will make sure
you don't spend one night in jail.

132
00:40:35.583 --> 00:40:39.083
Grace just sent a copy of your statement.

133
00:40:41.000 --> 00:40:42.416
Do you want to see it?

134
00:40:42.500 --> 00:40:43.500
There's no need.

135
00:40:43.583 --> 00:40:45.083
I know what it will say.

136
00:40:54.750 --> 00:40:57.083
What will you do if they deny it?

137
00:41:24.166 --> 00:41:25.875
Don't let us down again.

138
00:42:13.333 --> 00:42:15.250
Phila. where's Zinhle?

139
00:42:16.916 --> 00:42:18.000
And Kolobe?

140
00:42:18.916 --> 00:42:20.541
He'll meet us at the hall.

141
00:42:21.291 --> 00:42:22.416
I'm ready.

142
00:42:22.500 --> 00:42:25.083
Grace. I'm sorry for leaving yesterday.

143
00:42:26.791 --> 00:42:28.833
- Let's go.
- Where is Zinhle going?

144
00:42:30.458 --> 00:42:33.541
Zinhle works for us.
in case you forgot. Let's go. Zinhle.

145
00:42:59.958 --> 00:43:01.041
Are you ready?

146
00:43:08.541 --> 00:43:09.958
Tell me something.

147
00:43:18.041 --> 00:43:19.666
Why did you do it?

148
00:43:22.625 --> 00:43:25.416
Why are you still in touch with them?

149
00:43:25.500 --> 00:43:27.500
Why are you still in business with them?

150
00:43:32.000 --> 00:43:33.000
Love.

151
00:46:55.416 --> 00:46:56.875
Don kidnapped Kolobe.

152
00:46:56.958 --> 00:46:59.000
There's a tablet in there.

153
00:46:59.083 --> 00:47:00.416
What am I looking for?

154
00:47:00.500 --> 00:47:02.708
We're tracking Kolobe's location.

155
00:47:02.791 --> 00:47:04.500
I'm tracking his phone.

156
00:47:45.791 --> 00:47:48.000
- Where do we go?
- This way.

157
00:47:51.500 --> 00:47:53.041
Faster.

158
00:47:56.458 --> 00:47:57.500
Over there.

159
00:47:59.916 --> 00:48:01.541
There's no one inside.

160
00:48:05.541 --> 00:48:06.666
Stop here.

161
00:48:06.750 --> 00:48:09.875
His location says he's 500m
east behind the building.

162
00:48:14.166 --> 00:48:15.958
Zinhle. wait. Whoa. Zinhle!

163
00:48:40.958 --> 00:48:42.500
For the rest of my life.

164
00:48:52.791 --> 00:48:54.500
If this is my fate. I accept it.

165
00:48:54.583 --> 00:48:58.208
- Just give me the gun.
- But yours. yours is coming.
